Firm Level:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Demand for labor can increase while firm is investing in robots
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
More productive firms install more robots 
\emph on
in the steady state
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Labor is hired in 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

bursts
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 to cope with positive shocks
