Output of each sector (e.g., automotive) is aggregate from continuum of firms
 described above:
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
x_{s}\equiv\int Q\left(L_{s}^{\star}(R,z),R,u_{s}^{\star}(R,z),z\right)\textrm{d}G_{s}(R,z)\qquad\forall s
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

